oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bisbee's Comedians (proof)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Carnivals; Color separation;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color half sheet (blue on white) announcing the 37th Annual Tour of, presumably, Bisbee's Comedians, presented by Billy "Toby" Choate, featuring a tent theatre deluxe with all new plays and vaudeville. The poster features the first application of color in what would have been a two color poster. It is probably a proof.
